 smuggling, and the role of family expectations, emotions, and values in migrants' choices of destinations.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aAfricansxMigrationsxSocial aspects. 0aAnthropology. 0aEritreansxSocial aspectszEurope. 0aSociology (General). 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Emigration & Immigration.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2020 Englishz978311070472308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780520970755zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520970755zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520970755/original  a978-3-11-066763-9 University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-070471-6 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070472-3 EBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2020 Englishb2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-SEWb2020